      "title": "Two shootings in Gampaha and Ahungalla kills one, injured another",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A businessman was killed and another person was injured in two separate shootings which took place in Gampaha and Ahungalla today.",
        "Police said the two men who arrived on a motorcycle had opened fire to a bussinessman at Batapotha, Udugampola in Gampaha. He had died on admission to the Gampaha Hospital.",
        "Meanwhile, another two men arrived on a motorcycle had shot a man at Katuwila in Ahungalla.",
        "Police said the victim was admitted to the Balapitiya Hospital with wounds."
      ],
